All participants must join the Oho.ai's official Telegram Group.2. All participants must join BountyStar's  Telegram Group.3. Talking about the bounty in the project chat group will lead to immediate disqualification from the campaign and an instant ban from the company chat group. Please ask your bounty-related questions in the BountyStar's Group.4. KYC is not required for the bounty campaign. However, the project's team has the right to require KYC for suspicious cases.5. Please note that any offensive or inappropriate behavior will lead to immediate disqualification from the campaign.6. Using multiple accounts, cheating and spamming are not allowed.7. All participants must send the Proof of Authentication post to join the bounty program.Proof Of Registration Post Format: Code:#PROOF OF REGISTRATIONForum Username:Forum Profile Link:Telegram Username:ETH Wallet Address (Multichain supported):Rewards:  15 USD in OHORules:  1. Every participant must visit OHO's ANN, Website, Telegram for learning purpose.2. Participants should write a review on OHO's ANN or on this thread. (Giving feedback on OHO's ANN is most appreciated but it’s not mandatory)3. Participants should write a review on Telegram4. Participants can ask any question on OHO's ANN and Telegram Group. 5. Your Feedback/Review should be a minimum of 200 characters long6. Don't spam by doing copy paste. You have to mention point by point on your review. Like- which thing of OHO's you liked most, discussing and reviewing products, etc.7. Doing spam message can be cause of your parmanant ban. How to join:1. Join the Oho.ai's official Telegram Group 2.
